high_descs: turn right and walk over to the bath tub on the left
grab the dirty wash cloth out of the bath tub there
turn around and walk over to the bathroom sink at the end of the room towards the right a bit
place the cloth inside of the sink to clean it off, once you have cleaned it off take it back out
turn around to face the bathroom toilet which will then be right in front of you
place the cloth on top of the back side of the toilet there
anns.task_desc: place a clean cloth on top of the back side of the toilet

high_descs: Turn around to walk towards the bathtub.
Pick up a white rag from the bathtub.
Turn around to walk towards the sink on the opposite wall.
Rinse the white rag in the sink, removing it again.
Turn around to face the toilet.
Set the white rag down on the lid of the toilet tank.
anns.task_desc: Rinse a white rag from the bathtub to put it on the lid of the toilet tank.

high_descs: Turn right and walk to the tub to your left.
Grab the dirty rag inside the tub.
Turn left and walk to the sink to your left.
Place the dirty rag inside the sink, wash it and remove it.
Turn around to face the toilet.
Place the clean rag on top of the toilet.
anns.task_desc: Place a clean rag on top of the toilet.
